Package: tidytableR
Type: Package
Title: Builds Tables from Tidy Datasets
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Stephen Gragg
Maintainer: Stephen Gragg <graggsd@gmail.com>
Description: The purpose of this package is to reshape the output of an analysis
    from a tidy format into a for suitable for presentation. It allows users to 
    map column names from an input data frame to elements of an output table.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
